---
layout: recipe
title: Mulled Cider
author: jpatel
category: drinks
yield: ~6 servings
---
* 1 gal apple cider
* 1 orange
* 1 lemon
* 2-3 cinnamon sticks
* 1 tsp whole clove
* 1-2 tsp whole allspice
* pinch or two of grated ginger
* 2 star anise
* juniper berries (optional)
* 1 1/2 oz dark spiced Rum per cup (optional)

Start heating up the cider
Zest most of the orange and lemon as possible
Juice orange and lemon, optionally reserve a slice or two from each for garnish
Add spices, let mull, and enjoy!
